## Proposed Changes

### Database (Prisma)

#### [MODIFY] [schema.prisma](file:///d:/Work/App/backend/prisma/schema.prisma)
- Change datasource provider to `sqlite` and url to `file:./dev.db`.
- Remove PostgreSQL-specific `@db.Decimal(10,2)` annotations.
- Add scheduling and location fields to the `Order` model:
  - `address`: String (doorstep address)
  - `latitude`: Float (optional)
  - `longitude`: Float (optional)
  - `scheduledDate`: String (date e.g., "2026-05-28")
  - `scheduledSlot`: String (timeslot e.g., "11:00 AM - 01:00 PM")

