## Verification Plan

### Automated Verification
- Run local NestJS backend build to verify Prisma client generation and compilation.
- Run frontend build (`npm run build`) to ensure type safety.

### Manual Verification
- Book an order for tomorrow at "09:00 AM - 11:00 AM".
- Open a new window (or simulate another user booking) and select the same date.
- Verify that the "09:00 AM - 11:00 AM" slot is disabled and cannot be selected.
- Verify the tracking screen loads successfully after booking without ID parsing exceptions.
